                    "id": "0703fc40-6b81-45ee-9d76-c8e43e99df21",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "416ab4ce-df06-4afc-9df4-dca2121d7e4e",
                            "text": "Look at the Book",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "c3f5fcc7-0ba5-4afb-bc6e-10086e089708",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "It's a book about Lord Oelwyn. Seems like a very thick book for such a young subject.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "adc6509c-0bd0-45bd-bc95-a981d33487c0",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Oh, and it's only Volume 1!",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "389babdc-d018-4544-8459-bbf92d7843af",
                            "text": "Read the Book",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "4a7b1185-6432-49fe-85f4-c7f3f7d1fc33",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "It looks like Oelwyn, as a very young boy, showed a great aptitude for swordplay. Apparently, he conquered his school's entire second grade class... while he was still in Kindergarten! You go, boy!",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.playSoundEffect",
                                    "soundEffectName": "book_page_turn.wav",
                                    "wait": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "cc249fdb-e359-46cd-871e-c99fa49aa71a",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Apparently a friend and his entire family was lost when their boat was attacked by Cecil, a legendary monstrous seasick sea serpent. Ever since then, Oelwyn devoted himself to ridding the seas of these foul, merciless beasts.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d8b8dbc4-a1fa-4e0d-836a-f61a2776dfad",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Then, when he was seven, he started stowing away aboard fishing ships. By the time he was nine, he'd killed over twenty sea serpents... including Cecil! And he didn't even use a sword, he bashed Cecil in the head with rocks! Incredible!",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeTags",
                                    "id": "2c53cf4b-095d-462d-9c1d-c0981bea11fe",
                                    "scope": "prop",
                                    "scopeId": "11f50ec4-c9be-41d8-a042-5fe15c8fcc3d",
                                    "scopeFilterId": "25782df1-4461-4651-9bab-1fb4e1b4e366",
                                    "tagsToAdd": "ShawnHasRead",
                                    "tagsToRemove": null
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": true,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "c40dd96c-2cf6-44b9-8581-ad55317ce66f",
                            "text": "Steal the Book",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "24ac8a48-d4a2-4023-98fc-264fd2afdc58",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Hmm. The rapscallion in me says steal it, but the thief in me says it's not valuable or useful enough to bother stealing.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
